Bagaimanapun, kalian boleh pergi.

00:04:47.920 --> 00:04:48.880
Sebentar.

00:04:51.880 --> 00:04:53.400
Tidak apa-apa, Suraj.

00:04:53.600 --> 00:04:55.040
Kita akan makan siang bersama.

00:04:55.160 --> 00:04:56.360
Kesar.

