00:08:29.680 --> 00:08:30.680
Apa?

00:08:31.800 --> 00:08:34.640
Kabir, aku mencintaimu.

00:08:45.120 --> 00:08:47.760
Aku sangat mencintaimu, Kabir.
Aku mencintaimu.

